data.title: H.D. Jacobs Tennis
data.text:
Languages Spoken: English-ish. Not Swahili. !?Spanish?! I can clap fluently in several languages.

How did you get involved in tennis?

It was a bright cold day in April, and the clocks were striking thirteen...

How do you prepare for a big match?

A magician never reveals his secrets.

Flight or Invisibility? The power to refill things.

Favorites: FavoUrites

(non-tennis) Sport: Underwater Hockey

Hobbies: Singing, staying awake, sleeping, drawing, EATING

School Subject(S): and all peasants are loved, I can't pick just one.

TV Show: Netflix...ALL

Movie: Finding Nemo & The Lion King

Band and/or Song: Marvelous Breadfish (the song)

Tennis Player (why?):

Rachel Schillmoeller (Sidenote, Rachel, you owe me $30 now.)

Ice Cream Flavor: Why are you asking such difficult questions?!?

Old-School Cartoon: I never watched cartoons in school.
